Just because I can, here is some utterly gratuitous $\LaTeX$ (the nozzle exit velocity $v2$ of a nozzle):
$$
\begin{aligned}
v2 &= \sqrt{2gJ(h_1 - h_2) + v_1^2} \\
v2 &= \sqrt{\frac{2gk}{k - 1}RT_1\left[1 - \left(\frac{p_2}{p_1} \right) ^ \frac{(k-1)}{k} \right] + v_1^2}
\end{aligned}
$$
